1369047619,42057.0,出现次数:1\n", "unique_entities": {"pod_name": ["cartservice-0", "cartservice-1", "cartservice-2", "checkoutservice-0", "checkoutservice-2", "emailservice-0", "emailservice-1", "frontend-2", "recommendationservice-1"], "service_name": ["cartservice", "checkoutservice", "emailservice", "frontend", "recommendationservice", "redis"], "node_name": ["aiops-k8s-01", "aiops-k8s-03", "aiops-k8s-04", "aiops-k8s-05", "aiops-k8s-07", "aiops-k8s-08"]}, "status_combinations": "node_name,service_name,parent_pod,child_pod,operation_name,status_code,status_message,occurrence_count\naiops-k8s-05,checkoutservice,checkoutservice-2,checkoutservice-2,hipstershop.EmailService/SendOrderConfirmation,14,\"connection error: desc = \"\"transport: Error while dialing dial tcp: lookup emailservice on 10.233.33.139:53: server misbehaving\"\"\",出现次数:48\n", "matched_anomaly": "Please analyze the abnormal event between 2025-06-20T14:10:30Z and 2025-06-20T14:34:30Z and provide the root cause.", "time_range": "2025-06-20 14:10:30+00:00 to 2025-06-20 14:34:30+00:00"}, "trace_data_collected": true, "log_analysis_findings": "日志分析成功，我将基于检索到的详细信息进行分析，以判断待验证假设的成立性。\n\n### 日志详情\n- **服务**: `checkoutservice`\n- **问题描述**:\n  ```\n  failed to send order confirmation to \"someone@example.com\": rpc error: code = Unavailable desc = connection error: desc = \"transport: Error while dialing dial tcp: lookup emailservice on 10.233.33.139:53: server misbehaving\"\n  ```\n- **错误频次**: 48 次\n- **日志关键词提取**: `dns`, `transport`, `Error while dialing`\n\n### 错误模式识别\n1. **DNS 故障模式**:\n   - 错误包含 `\"transport: Error while dialing dial tcp: lookup emailservice on ...\"`.\n   - 目标服务 `emailservice` 的 DNS 查询失败。\n   - 日志内明确提到 `server misbehaving`。\n\n### 验证结论\n基于以上分析，假设与该错误相关，根因可以被识别为 DNS 配置问题，涉及 `emailservice` 的查询错误。\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"SUPPORT\",\n  \"detected_log_keys\": [\"dns\", \"transport\", \"Error while dialing\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"checkoutservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"DNS 配置错误导致无法解析 emailservice 的主机名。\",\n      \"evidence\": \"failed to send order confirmation to \\\"someone@example.com\\\": rpc error: code = Unavailable desc = connection error: desc = \\\"transport: Error while dialing dial tcp: lookup emailservice on 10.233.33.139:53: server misbehaving\\\"\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```", "metric_analysis_findings": "### 分析结果\n对 UUID `bc7e1bf2-405` 的指标数据分析表明异常主要集中在 `checkoutservice` 服务的指标上，特别是 `error_ratio` 和 `rrt_max` 指标发生显著变化。\n\n### 异常指标\n从 CSV 数据中提取出绝对变化最显著的指标：\n- `error_ratio` (checkoutservice): 从 0.0% 上升到 34.04%，变化率 2.0\n- `server_error_ratio` (checkoutservice): 从 0.0% 上升到 34.04%，变化率 2.0\n- `rrt_max` (checkoutservice): 从 193255.0 增加到 3214328.5，变化率 1.7731\n\n### 根因假设\n1. **异常组件**: `checkoutservice-2`\n2. **异常原因**: 在指标数据中，`checkoutservice-2` 服务的 `error_ratio` 和 `rrt_max` 表现出显著的变化，表明该服务的延迟和错误率急剧增加，可能与该服务的某个功能模块或服务调用的失败有关。\n3. **证据**: \n   - `checkoutservice-2` 的 `error_ratio` 从 0.0% 上升到 34.04%\n   - `checkoutservice-2` 的 `rrt_max` 从 193255.0 增加到 3214328.5\n\n### 验证判断\n该根因假设得到了指标数据的支持。\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"SUPPORT\",\n  \"detected_metric_keys\": [\"error_ratio\", \"server_error_ratio\", \"rrt_max\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"checkoutservice-2\",\n      \"reason\": \"Error ratio and response time max increased significantly indicating potential failures in the service operations or dependencies.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"error_ratio from 0.0% to 34.04%, rrt_max from 193255.0 to 3214328.5\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```", "trace_analysis_findings": "根据异常调用链数据，我们可以从以下几点进行分析：\n\n### 延迟分析\n1. **Frontend to CheckoutService**: 平均异常延迟从正常的 156,733 微秒增加到 2,732,283 微秒，延迟倍数为 17.43。\n2. **CheckoutService to EmailService**: 平均异常延迟从正常的 20,201 微秒增加到 2,538,290 微秒，延迟倍数为 125.60。\n\n### 错误类型\n- **EmailService** 出现了 `connection error`，描述为 `server misbehaving`。这通常表明 EmailService 无法正常工作。\n\n### 关键发现提取\n- 延迟指标：显著延迟存在于 Frontend 和 CheckoutService 的关系上，以及 CheckoutService 和 EmailService 的关系上。\n- 错误状态：EmailService 报告了连接错误，表明该服务可能无法正常运行。\n\n### 根因定位\n1. **CheckoutService 与 EmailService**: EmailService 的连接错误表明它无法正常响应，这可能是造成整个事务链条延迟的根因。\n2. **因果关系**: EmailService 是 CheckoutService 的下游，且同时 CheckoutService 和 EmailService 都出现了异常，EmailService 应属于根因而不是受害者。\n\n### 输出 JSON\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"SUPPORT\",\n  \"detected_trace_keys\": [\"latency_spike\", \"checkoutservice->emailservice\", \"connection_refused\", \"slow_response\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"EmailService\",\n      \"reason\": \"异常原因可能是 EmailService 出现了连接错误，导致其无法正常响应请求。\",\n      \"evidence\": \"连接错误消息：connection error: desc = \\\"transport: Error while dialing dial tcp: lookup emailservice on 10.233.33.139:53: server misbehaving\\\"\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\nEmailService 的连接错误和导致的延迟问题支持当前假设，即 EmailService 是异常事件的根因。", "current_hypothesis": "checkoutservice is the root cause due to DNS configuration error preventing resolution of emailservice hostname."}
